aje%20-%20are%20also%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20much-anticipated%20announcement%2C%20the%20BJP%20this%20evening%20released%20the%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates.%20The%20list%20includes%20PM%20Modi%20from%20his%20constituency%20Varanasi%20and%2034%20ministers%20from%20the%20Centre%20and%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20finalised%2024%20names%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20was%20replaced%20by%20the%20party%20leadership%20as%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20Mohan%20Yadav%20after%20assembly%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Vidisha%20constituency.%20This%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20win%20for%20Mr%20Chouhan%20who%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20was%20offered%20the%20Bhopal%20seat%20which%20he%20rejected%20and%20conveyed%20his%20desire%20to%20fight%20from%20Vidisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20BJP's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20(CEC)%20met%20on%20Thursday%20night%20to%20deliberate%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20(NDA)%20won%20a%20total%20of%20303%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20behind%20at%2052%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709390580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F26i4t0u_jyotiraditya-scindia-amit-shah-ani_625x300_02_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-union-minister-jyotiraditya-scindia-named-for-lok-sabha-seat-he-lost-to-bjp-in-2019-polls-5163739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Aviation%20Minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20will%20be%20contesting%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Guna%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20seat%20he%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen