%20and%20got%20him%20fit%20to%20play%20Ranji.%C2%A0There%20are%20only%20one%20or%20two%20exceptions%20who%20need%20to%20be%20spoken%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20that%20with%20the%20dropping%20of%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20central%20contracts%2C%20whether%20the%20ficus%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20relevance%20of%20first-class%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20someone%20has%20not%20played%20or%20ignored%20red-ball%20domestic%20cricket.%20Otherwise%2C%20all%20of%20them%20have%20played%20Ranji%20Trophy%20when%20they%20were%20free.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20BCCI%20will%20take%20proper%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Shah%20has%20earlier%20mentioned%20Ishan%20Kishan%20during%20an%20interaction%20but%20quickly%20added%20that%20the%20announcement%20was%20not%20targeted%20towards%20him%20and%20this%20rule%20will%20apply%20for%20all%20cricketers%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20contracted%20players%20have%20been%20told%20on%20phone%20and%20I'll%20be%20writing%20to%20them%20too.%20If%20chairman%20of%20selectors%2C%20coach%20%26amp%3B%20captain%20want%20you%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20then%20you%20gotta%20play.%20'Nakhre%20Nahi%20Chalenge'%20(no%20tantrums).%20And%20as%20far%20as%20Ishan%20Kishan%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20is%20young%2C%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20specifically%20about%20him%20as%20it%20will%20be%20applicable%20for%20all%20the%20players%20uniformly%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Shah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20otherwise%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20given%20me%20his%20suggestions%20and%20I%20am%20g