0Anderson's%20Blockbuster%20Comment%20On%20India%20Star's%20Absence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEngland's%20experienced%20right-arm%20seamer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22James%20Anderson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F517-james-anderson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJames%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20just%20two%20more%20scalps%20away%20from%20700%20Test%20wickets%20as%20he%20prepares%20himself%20for%20the%20fifth%20Test%20of%20the%20ongoing%20five-match%20Test%20series%20against%20India.%20The%20fifth%20Test%20starts%20in%20Dharamsala%20on%20Thursday.%20Anderson%20has%20snapped%20a%20total%20of%20698%20wickets%20so%20far%20in%20186%20Tests%20at%20an%20average%20of%2026.51%20where%20he%20has%20conceded%20runs%20at%20an%20economy%20of%202.79%20with%2032%20four-wicket%20hauls%20and%2032%20five-wicket%20hauls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20completes%20this%20landmark%2C%20he%20will%20become%20the%20first%20seamer%20to%20do%20so%20and%20third%20overall%20after%20legendary%20spinners%20Muttiah%20Murlidharan%20(800)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shane%20Warne%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F437-shane-warne-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShane%20Warne%3C%2Fa%3E%20(708).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20fifth%20Test%2C%20Anderson%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20thoughts%20about%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20India%20vs%20England%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20English%20fans%20will%20be%20thankful%20he's%20not%20playing%20because%20he's%20such%20a%20quality%20player.%20But%20from%20our%20point%20of%20view%20you%20want%20to%20test%20yourself%2C%20you%20want%20to%20come%20up%20against%20the%20best%20and%20he's%20been%20someone%20who%20I've%20found%20really%20challenging%20to%20bowl%20at%20over%20the%20years%20and%20it's%20a%20shame%20he's%20not%20been%20playing%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Anderson%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20that%20reverse%20swing%20can%20play%20a%20big%20part%20in%20India%20and%20he's%20(Bumrah)%20a%20great%20exponent%20of%20it.%20That%20yorker%20we%20saw%20to%20Ollie%20Pope%2C%20he's%20got%20that%20up%20his%20sleeve%20as%20well.%20It's%20not%20a%20fluke%20that%20he's%20got%20to%20number%20one%20in%20the%20world.%20He's%20a%20world-class%20bowler%20and%20from%20our%20point%20of%20view%20we%20weren't%20surprised%20that%20he%20put%20up%20a%20performance%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2041%2C%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0continues%20to%20lead%20the%20England%20attack.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Zaheer%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F257-zaheer-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EZaheer%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20someone%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20a%20lot%20to%20try%20and%20learn%20from.%20How%20he%20used%20the%20reverse%20swing%2C%20how%20he%20covered%20the%20ball%20when%20he%20ran%20into%20bowl%2C%20that's%20something%20I%20tried%20to%20sort%20of%20develop%20on%20the%20back%20of%20playing%20against%20him%20quite%20a%20few%20times%20here%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0told%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaheer%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20finest%20seamers%2C%20played%20his%20last%20Test%20in%202014%20when%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20game.%20Among%20the%20current%20lot%20of%20Indian%20pacers%2C%C2%A0Anderson%C2%A0is%20most%20impressed%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E's%20ability%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20exponent%26quot%3B%20of%20reverse%20swing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709388720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F70vft8do_james-anderson-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_24_F