%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20legal%20areas%2C%20including%20disputes%20involving%20contracts%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20tax%2C%20international%20commercial%20arbitrations%2C%20and%20criminal%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20Swaraj%20made%20headlines%20last%20year%20when%20she%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20over%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20During%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20she%20characterized%20the%20AAP%20government%20as%20%26quot%3Bjhagdalu%20(quarrelsome)%20and%20nikammi%20(useless)%2C%26quot%3B%20criticizing%20their%20perceived%20inefficiency%20since%202015.%20She%20congratulated%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20for%20passing%20the%20Bill%2C%20expressing%20confidence%20that%20the%20administration%20in%20Delhi%20would%20now%20operate%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoping%20to%20get%20a%20massive%20first-mover%20advantage%20as%20it%20works%20towards%20its%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20today%20announced%20a%20list%20of%20195%20candidates%20even%20before%20the%20poll%20dates%20have%20been%20notified.%20The%20list%20includes%20the%20party's%20heaviest%20hitters%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20Varanasi%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20will%20be%20fielded%20again%20from%20Gandhinagar%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709387400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F3f9rrnv4_bansuri-swaraj_625x300_02_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-bjp-list-sushma-swaraj-daughter-bansuri-swaraj-to-make-her-poll-debut-5163312%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20foreign%20affairs%20minister%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20is