%20Research%20strategist%20Ed%20Clissold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20surged%20nearly%208%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20extending%20last%20year's%20strong%20rally%20driven%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-outlook-recession-inflation-grocery-prices-vibecession-paul-krugman-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DInflation%2520has%2520cooled%2520dramatically%2520from%2Cpast%2520few%2520years%252C%2520economists%2520say.%5C%22%3Econtinued%20disinflation%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20outlook%20for%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-outlook-pandemic-stock-market-crash-inflation-recession-rates-ai-2024-2%5C%22%3Eand%20solid%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20those%20factors%2C%20if%20they%20persist%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20could%20help%20give%20Biden%20a%20boost%20in%20his%20approval%20ratings%2C%20which%20have%20been%20weighed%20down%20various%20issues%20including%20elevated%20inflation%2C%20his%20age%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frashida-tlaib-uncommitted-biden-israel-gaza-michigan-primary-2024-2%5C%22%3Ehis%20stance%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20usually%20been%20weak%20in%20the%20early%20year%20of%20a%20Presidential%20election%2C%20with%20a%20median%20drop%20of%201%25%2C%20but%20when%20an%20incumbent%20party%20wins%20the%20election%20in%20November%2C%20the%20early%20part%20of%20the%20year%20sees%20an%20average%20gain%20rather%20than%20a%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20an%20incumbent%20Democrat%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20win%2C%20the%20DJIA%20has%20risen%20a%20median%20of%202.6%25%20in%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20the%20year%20versus%20a%206.2%25%20decline%20when%20an%20incumbent%20Democrat%20has%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20Clissold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClissold%20acknowledges%20that%20two%20months%20of%20stock%20market%20performance%20is%20by%20no%20means%20a%20determining%20factor%20of%20a%20Presidential%20election%2C%20but%20it's%20interesting%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20two-month%20window%20eight%20months%20before%20the%20election%20is%20hardly%20the%20most%20robust%20indicator%2C%20especially%20considering%20how%20many%20factors%20beyond%20the%20stock%20market%20go%20into%20voters'%20decision-making%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Clissold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20if%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20rising%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%20election%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20means%20the%20economy%20is%20doing%20well%20and%20consumer%20confidence%20is%20improving%2C%20so%20that%20backdrop%20could%20ultimately%20provide%20a%20tailwind%20to%20Biden's%20re-election%20chances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%2030%2C000-foot%20perspective%2C%20a%20better%20economic%20backdrop%20would%20help%20Biden's%20chances%2C%26quot%3B%20Clissold%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-signal-presidential-reelection-joe-biden-incumbent-donald-trump-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709387161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e21a19ce7f1785b2e57ab3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-signal-presidential-reelection-joe-biden-incumbent-donald-trump-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20strong%20start%20to%20the%20year%20for%20stocks%20has%20tended%20to%20foreshadow%20an%20incumbent%20victory%2C%20especially%20for%20Democrats%2C%26quot%3B%20Ned%20Davis%20Research%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-signal-presidential-reelecti