20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Ftypes-of-ocd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20OCD%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20simply%20could%20not%20entrust%20my%20husband%20with%20the%20tasks%20related%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20our%20home.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20an%20absolute%20blast%20to%20live%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20years%2C%20I%20was%20an%20ambitious%20woman%20at%20the%20start%20of%20my%20career%2C%20plucking%20away%20at%20my%20laptop%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20hours%2C%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bboss%20babe.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20not%20a%20traditional%20wife%20%E2%80%94%20or%20tradwife%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20rarely%20cooked%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdidnt-want-kids-relationship-changed-my-mind-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escoffed%20at%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20did%20as%20I%20pleased.%20I%20thought%20little%20of%20caring%20for%20my%20husband.%20Not%20because%20I%20didn't%20care%20%3Cem%3Eabout%3C%2Fem%3E%20him%2C%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20I%20cared%20about%20him%20quite%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20my%20main%20focus%20was%20on%20working%20and%20paying%20bills.%20I%20wasn't%20about%20to%20play%20the%20doting%20housewife%20on%20top%20of%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20at%2039%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-childless-want-husband-family-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle%2C%20and%20childless%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20priorities%20have%20completely%20shifted%2C%20and%20my%20career%20pursuits%20no%20longer%20fulfill%20me.%20I'm%20honestly%20not%20sure%20if%20they%20ever%20did.%20I%20feel%20like%20I've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20collecting%20material%20things%20that%20don't%20make%20me%20happy%2C%20having%20hollow%20experiences%20with%20people%20I%20had%20no%20future%20with%2C%20and%20clinging%20to%20the%20freedom%20I