ities%2Fchandigarh%2Fat-least-3-farmers-lost-vision-due-to-pellet-injuries-punjab-health-minister-9164170%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20result%20of%20pellet%20gun%20injuries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20several%20had%20their%20faces%20disfigured%20by%20the%20gunshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubkaran%20Singh%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Bhatinda%2C%20died%20from%20head%20injuries%20last%20week%2C%20with%20his%20family%20and%20farmer%20groups%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Fshubhkaran-singh-death-bullet-injury-farmers-protest-fir-details%5C%22%3Emaintaining%20he%20was%20shot.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Much%20before%20the%20protests%20began%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%E2%80%99s%20preparations%20gave%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20far%20the%20state%20would%20go%20to%20prevent%20a%20movement%20from%20taking%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20DGP%20of%20Haryana%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fharyana-dgp-denies-using-pellet-guns-against-protesting-farmers%2Farticle67860605.ece%5C%22%3Edenied%20using%20pellets%20on%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20medical%20injuries%20sustained%20give%20us%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20spectacular%20nature%20of%20violence%20against%20farmers%20protesting%20peacefully%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20crossings%20of%20Khanuari%20and%20Shambhu%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20instance%20of%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20in%20India%20was%20witnessed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202010.%20In%202016%2C%20following%20the%20protests%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20encounter%20of%20Hizbul%20commander%20Burhan%20Wani%2C%20the%20police%20resorted%20to%20excessive%20pellet%20actions%2C%20injuring%20hundreds%20of%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20High%20Court%20regarding%20the%20usage%20of%20pellet%20guns%2C%20and%20the%20court%20refused%20to%20put%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20its%20use.%20In%20the%20year%202017%2C%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Bar%20Association%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20for%20a%20blanket%20prohibition%20on%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20weapons%2C%20which%20asked%20the%20high%20court%20to%20expedite%20the%20matter.%20It%20was%20in%202020%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fj-k%2Fj-k-high-court-refuses-to-ban-use-of-pellet-guns-in-kashmir-53869%5C%22%3Ehigh%20court%20finally%20dismissed%20the%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20upholding%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20by%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20reasoned%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20protest%20is%20not%20peaceful%20and%20security%20personnel%20are%20attacked%20by%20violent%20mobs%2C%20they%20have%20to%20use%20force%20in%20self-defense.%E2%80%9D%20Further%2C%20regarding%20the%20nature%20of%20force%2C%20it%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20kind%20of%20force%20has%20to%20be%20used%20at%20a%20relevant%20point%20in%20time%20or%20in%20a%20given%20situation%20and%20place%20has%20to%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20persons%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20place%20where%20the%20attack%20is%20happening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20rejected%20the%20appeal%20by%20referring%20to%20force%20mostly%20in%20vague%20terms%20without%20addressing%20the%20issue%20of%20pellets.%20However%2C%20it%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20has%20formed%20an%20expert%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%20The%20report%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20made%20public%2C%20did%20not%20prohibit%20its%20usage%20but%20recommended%20that%20it%20be%20used%20as%20a%20last%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20is%20now%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20April%20this%20year.%20The%20petition%20challenges%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20on%20account%20of%20them%20being%20%E2%80%98indiscriminatory%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20how%20they%20target%20people.%20What%20is%20meant%20by%20this%20%E2%80%98indiscriminate%E2%80%99%20nature%20is%20that%20when%20a%20pellet%20gun%20is%20fired%2C%20100%20pellets%20that%20are%20lethal%20are%20sprayed%20in%20all%20directions%2C%20where%20men%2C%20women%2C%20children%2C%20and%20even%20innocent%20bystanders%20watching%20the%20events%20are%20blinded%2C%20injured%2C%20and%20sometimes%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20treating%20pellet%20victims%20have%20stated%20that%20it%20maims%20a%20person%20forever%2C%20causing%20partial%20or%20complete%20blindness.%20The%20spread%20and%20proclivity%20for%20their%20usage%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20degree%20of%20destruction%20caused%2C%20are%20unparalleled%2C%20making%20them%20unsuitable%20for%20managing%20the%20crowd%20as%20their%20operators%20cannot%20effectively%20control%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%98indiscriminate%E2%80%99%20character%20of%20pellets%20violates%20the%20UN%20Basic%20Principles%2C%20which%20specify%20that%20the%20use%20of%20force%20to%20disperse%20nonviolent%20unlawful%20assemblies%20should%20be%20avoided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDissecting%20the%20pellet%20and%20the%20law%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPellet%20guns%2C%20made%20of%20metals%20that%20resemble%20ball%20bearings%2C%20are%20classified%20as%20Kinetic%20Impact%20Projectiles%20(KIPs)%2C%20which%20include%20weapons%20that%20cannot%20be%20aimed%20at%20specific%20targets%20but%20scatter%20ammunition%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20risks%20connected%20with%20KIPs%20include%20death%20or%20major%20injury%20to%20the%20head%2C%20upper%20body%2C%20or%20susceptible%20area%20if%20struck%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20projectiles%20penetrating%20the%20body%2C%20and%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20injuring%20innocent%20bystanders%20due%20to%20projectile%20inaccuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20international%20law%2C%20the%20use%20of%20pellets%20is%20prohibited%20because%20it%20violates%20the%20norms%20of%20proportionality%20under%20international%20human%20rights%20law%20and%20customary%20international%20law.%20The%20UN%20Basic%20Principles%20on%20the%20Use%20of%20Force%20and%20Firearms%20by%20Law%20Enforcement%20Officials%2C%20adopted%20by%20the%20eighth%20United%20Nations%20Congress%20on%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Treatment%20of%20Offenders%20require%20the%20government%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20to%20consider%20the%20ethical%20issues%20associated%20with%20the%20use%20of%20force%20and%20firearms%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20proportionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fharyana-dgp-claims-rubber-bullets-not-pellet-guns-used-on-protesting-farmers%5C%22%3EHaryana%20DGP%20Claims%20Rubber%20Bullets%2C%20Not%20Pellet%20Guns%2C%20Used%20on%20Protesting%20Farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20development%20of%20non-lethal%20incapacitating%20weapons%20for%20use%20in%20specific%20scenarios.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20under%20rules%2070%20and%2071%2C%20prohibits%20the%20use%20of%20tools%20that%20are%20indiscriminate%20and%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20unnecessary%20pain%20or%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%20rules%2C%20even%20for%20warfare%2C%20do%20not%20accept%20attacks%20that%20may%20cause%20incidental%20loss%20of%20civilian%20life%2C%20injury%20to%20civilians%2C%20damage%20to%20civilian%20objects%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20thereof%20that%20is%20excessive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPellet%20action%20against%20the%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20are%20likewise%20constitutionally%20obligated%20to%20display%20fundamental%20restraint%20and%20act%20proportionally%20to%20their%20legitimate%20objectives%20that%20are%20to%20be%20achieved.%20It%20is%20consequently%20crucial%20to%20ask%20what%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20objective%20was%20in%20using%20force%20against%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssuming%20it%20was%20to%20prevent%20the%20farmers%20from%20marching%20to%20Delhi%2C%20then%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20what%20if%20the%20farmers%20had%20crossed%20the%20border%20and%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%3F%20Have%20the%20farmers%20not%20demonstrated%20enough%20that%20their%20protests%20have%20been%20extremely%20peaceful%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20completely%20aware%20that%20the%20protests%20are%20not%20intended%20to%20generate%20a%20public%20emergency%20or%20chaos%20in%20Delhi.%20The%202020%20farmer%20demonstrations%20have%20already%20given%20us%20the%20most%20powerful%20example%20of%20non-violent%20protests%20in%20the%20recent%20history%20of%20India.%20What%20explains%20the%20firing%20of%20tear%20gas%20shells%20from%20drones%20overhead%2C%20injuring%20hundreds%20of%20farmers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20elderly%20and%20have%20difficulty%20breathing%2C%20when%20a%20template%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20protest%20had%20already%20been%20established%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20question%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20asked%20here%20is%3A%20Was%20the%20use%20of%20cranes%2C%20boulders%2C%20and%20roadblocks%20to%20restrict%20the%20protestors%E2%80%99%20from%20exercising%20their%20constitutional%20rights%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20assembly%20not%20a%20force%20that%20the%20state%20performed%20right%20before%20the%20protests%20had%20begun%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20deploying%20pellet%20guns%20that%20left%20protesters%20permanently%20disabled%20and%20at%20risk%20of%20death%2C%20the%20state%20breached%20its%20commitment%20to%20protect%20and%20preserve%20human%20life.%20These%20violated%20both%20the%20constitutional%20requirement%20to%20protect%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights%20to%20life%20and%20health%20as%20well%20as%20the%20international%20laws%20that%20forbid%20such%20use%20in%20conflict%2C%20let%20alone%20in%20peaceful%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20is%20widely%20used%20to%20discredit%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20a%20standard%20instrument%20for%20criminalising%20dissent%20in%20democratic%20India.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20not%20let%20the%20usage%20of%20pellet%20guns%20be%20normalised%20in%20a%20peaceful%20citizen%20demonstration.%20Suppressing%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20with%20measures%20such%20as%20pellet%20guns%20assumes%20protestors%20are%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3Eviolent%20and%20unorganised%20mob%E2%80%99%20and%20attempts%20to%20disorganise%20an%20organised%20group%20of%20civilian%20protestors%20by%20using%20excessive%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20must%20see%20through%20the%20recent%20usage%20of%20pellet%20guns%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Delhi%20borders%20against%20the%20protestors%20and%20strike%20it%20down%20immediately.%20It%20must%20now%20hear%20the%20long-overdue%20petition%20and%20prohibit%20the%20use%20of%20pellet%20guns%20altogether%2C%20especially%20during%20civilian%20protests.%20This%20would%20reassert%20its%20constitutional%20obligation%20to%20protect%20and%20facilitate%20free%20expression%20and%20assembly%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKawalpreet%20Kaur%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141152%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.13-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-protest-has-shown-that-sc-must-strike-down-the-use-of-pellet-guns-with-a-sense-of-urgency%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20international%20law%2C%20the%20use%20of%20pellets%20is%20prohibited%20because%20it%20violates%20the%20norms%20of%20proportionality%20under%20international%20human%20rights%20law%20and%20customary%20international%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-protest-has-shown-that-sc-must-strike-down-the-use-of-pellet-guns-with-a-sense-of-urgency%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Honourable%20Exit%3F%20Why%20Two%20BJP%20MPs%20Said%20They%20Don't%20Want%20To%20Contest%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20Indian%20politics%2C%20where%20there%20is%20intense%20competition%20for%20tickets%20from%20any%20party%20that%20has%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%2C%20sitting%20MPs%20declaring%20that%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20contest%20again%20is%20rare.%20So%2C%20when%20two%20BJP%20MPs%20said%20-%20within%20hours%20of%20each%20other%20-%20today%20that%20they%20would%20like%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Brelieved%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20political%20duties%2C%20it%20took%20many%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20well-oiled%20election%20machinery%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20conducted%20extensive%20surveys%20and%20held%20long%20deliberations%20on%20every%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20had%20already%20decided%20not%20to%20repeat%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Jayant%20Sinha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20around%2010%20am%20today%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20from%20East%20Delhi%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20requested%20Hon'ble%20Party%20President%20%40JPNadda%20ji%20to%20relieve%20me%20of%20my%20political%20duties%20so%20that%20I%20can%20focus%20on%20my%20upcoming%20cricket%20commitments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20five%20hours%20later%2C%20Jayant%20Sinha%2C%20who%20represents%20Jharkhand's%20Hazaribagh%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20made%20a%20nearly%20identical%20post.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20requested%20Hon'ble%20Party%20President%20Shri%20%40JPNadda%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0ji%20to%20relieve%20me%20of%20my%20direct%20electoral%20duties%20so%20that%20I%20can%20focus%20my%20efforts%20on%20combating%20global%20climate%20change%20in%20Bharat%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20leaders%20also%20thanked%20the%20party's%20leadership%2C%20including%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20for%20the%20opportunities%20provided%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Gambhir%20is%20a%20first-time%20MP%2C%20while%20Jayant%20Sinha%2C%20son%20of%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Yashwant%20Sinha%20had%20been%20elected%20from%20Hazaribagh%20twice%20in%20a%20row.%20Sources%20indicated%20that%20both%20MPs%20were%20not%20very%20popular%20in%20their%20constituencies%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20set%20itself%20a%20target%20of%20winning%20a%20mammoth%20370%20seats%2C%20had%20decided%20not%20to%20repeat%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Delhi%2C%20where%20the%20party%20had%20won%20all%20seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20for%20new%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20followed%20a%20lengthy%2C%20detailed%20process%2C%20which%20included%20getting%20feedback%20from%20the%20people%20in%20every%20constituency%2C%20conducting%20internal%20evaluations%2C%20and%20hiring%20survey%20agencies%20to%20file%20comprehensive%20reports.%20These%20were%20followed%20by%20deliberations%20by%20the%20state%20leadership%20and%20the%20national%20brass.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20national%20leadership%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20MPs%20whose%20performance%20was%20not%20up%20to%20the%20mark%20would%20not%20be%20repeated%20and%20that%20at%20least%2060%20incumbent%20MPs%20could%20face%20this%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20night%2C%20a%20five-hour%20meeting%20had%20been%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20attended%20by%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Nadda%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20meeting%2C%20which%20began%20at%2011%20pm%20and%20ended%20at%204%20am%2C%20had%20also%20focused%20on%20constituencies%20that%20the%20party%20hadn't%20done%20well%20in.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20announce%20the%20names%20of%20the%20candidates%20even%20before%20the%20poll%20dates%20are%20out%2C%20so%20that%20they%20get%20enough%20time%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20voters%20in%20their%20respective%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20list%20of%20the%20candidates%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20released%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7lgmd7r_gautam-gambhir-jayant-sinha_625x300_02_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-gambhir-jayant-sinha-an-honourable-exit-why-two-bjp-mps-said-they-dont-want-to-contest-again-5162715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Indian%20politics%2C%20where%20there%20is%20intense%20competition%20for%20tickets%20from%20any%20party%20that%20has%20a%20chance%20of%20winning%2C%20sitting%20MPs%20declaring%20that%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20contest%20again%20is%20rare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-gambhir-jayant-sinha-an-honourable-exit-why-two-bjp-mps-said-they-dont-want-to-contest-again-5162715%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Landslides%20Hit%20Vital%20Jammu-Srinagar%20Highway%2C%20Traffic%20Blocked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Srinagar-Jammu%20national%20highway%2C%20a%20vital%20road%20that%20connects%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20is%20blocked%20after%20landslides%20and%20avalanches%20in%20multiple%20locations%20following%20heavy%20rain%20and%20snowfall%20in%20the%20region.%20A%20video%20of%20a%20massive%20landslide%20hitting%20the%20highway%20has%20surfaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meteorological%20department%20has%20predicted%20moderate%20rain%20and%20snowfall%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20this%20week%2C%20with%20peak%20activity%20on%20March%201%20and%202.%20The%20vital%20270-km%20long%20Srinagar-Jammu%20highways%20were%20closed%20after%20landslides%20at%20multiple%20places%2C%20particularly%20between%20Banihal%20and%20Ramban%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20from%20an%20unidentified%20location%20shows%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20mud%20and%20boulders%20rolling%20down%20the%20hill%20and%20falling%20on%20the%20highway.%20Within%20seconds%2C%20the%20debris%20blocked%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20highway.%20Road%20clearing%20operations%20are%20underway%2C%20till%20then%2C%20the%20movement%20on%20the%20highway%20remains%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20showed%20at%20least%20three%20JCB%20crawler%20machines%20deployed%20to%20clear%20the%20debris%20and%20a%20small%20stream%20of%20muddy%20water%20has%20formed.%20Another%20video%20showed%20trucks%20stranded%20on%20the%20highway%20and%20fast-flowing%20brown%2C%20muddy%20water%20moving%20down%20the%20hill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-altitude%20areas%20of%20the%20Jammu%20region%20recorded%20fresh%20snowfall%2C%20while%20the%20plains%2C%20including%20the%20winter%20capital%20city%20were%20lashed%20by%20rains%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFew%20places%20may%20experience%20heavy%20to%20very%20heavy%20snow%20particularly%20over%20higher%20reaches%20of%20the%20north%2C%20central%20and%20south%20Kashmir%20and%20Pirpanjal%20range%20of%20Jammu%20division%20during%20this%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20weather%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20plains%20of%20Kashmir%20may%20receive%20moderate%20rain%20or%20snow%20while%20the%20plains%20of%20Jammu%20may%20receive%20moderate%20rain%20with%20a%20possibility%20of%20heavy%20rain%20over%20Ramban%2C%20Udhampur%20and%20Reasi%20districts.%20Few%20places%20may%20experience%20thunder%2C%20lightning%20or%20hailstorms%20accompanied%20by%20gusty%20winds%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20traffic%20department%20official%20said%20the%20one-way%20traffic%20on%20the%20Jammu-Srinagar%20national%20highway%2C%20the%20only%20all-weather%20road%20linking%20Kashmir%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20was%20moving%20smoothly%20despite%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGulmarg%20and%20tourist%20resort%20towns%20Sonamarg%20and%20Doodhpathri%20received%20moderate%20to%20heavy%20snow.%20Gurez%2C%20Kupwara%2C%20Baltal%20and%20other%20towns%20in%20the%20higher%20reaches%20also%20received%20fresh%20snow.%20At%20present%2C%20it%20is%20raining%20or%20snowing%20moderately%20at%20most%20places%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Foa3hpflg_landslide-_625x300_02_March_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-landslides-hit-vital-jammu-srinagar-highway-traffic-blocked-5162711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Srinagar-Jammu%20national%20highway%2C%20a%20vital%20road%20that%20connects%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20is%20blocked%20after%20landslides%20and%20avalanches%20on%20multiple%20locations%20following%20heavy%20rain%20and%20snowfall%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-landslides-hit-vital-jammu-srinagar-highway-traffic-blocked-5162711%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-landslides-hit-vital-jammu-srinagar-highway-traffic-blocked-5162711%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-landslides-hit-vital-jammu-srinagar-highway-traffic-blocked-5162711%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Jogani%20vs%20Jogani'%3A%20How%20Dispute%20With%20Brothers%20Cost%20Tycoon%20Rs%2020%2C000%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%2021-year%20legal%20battle%20among%20five%20brothers%20from%20India%2C%20renowned%20for%20their%20success%20in%20the%20diamond%20trade%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20real%20estate%2C%20has%20reached%20a%20turning%20point%20with%20a%20groundbreaking%20verdict.%20Haresh%20Jogani%20has%20been%20ordered%20by%20a%20jury%20to%20pay%20over%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20damages%20to%20his%20brothers%2C%20Shashikant%2C%20Rajesh%2C%20Chetan%2C%20and%20Shailesh%20Jogani%2C%20and%20to%20divide%20their%20extensive%20Southern%20California%20property%20holdings%2C%20consisting%20of%20around%2017%2C000%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20legal%20dispute%2C%20known%20as%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-businessman-to-pay-over-rs-20-000-crore-to-his-brothers-heres-why-5160799%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709465450499000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1V_id8sfBtyXPG__aTmxoP%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-businessman-to-pay-over-rs-20-000-crore-to-his-brothers-heres-why-5160799%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Jogani%20v.%20Jogani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stems%20from%20accusations%20that%20Haresh%20Jogani%20violated%20a%20longstanding%20partnership%20with%20his%20siblings.%20This%20complex%20case%2C%20often%20likened%20to%20Charles%20Dickens'%20Bleak%20House%2C%20has%20endured%2018%20appeals%2C%20numerous%20attorneys%2C%20and%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20five%20judges%20in%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Superior%20Court.%20While%20the%20trial's%20main%20phase%20has%20ended%2C%20a%20punitive%20damages%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20Monday%20may%20further%20shape%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhat%20sets%20this%20case%20apart%20is%20its%20unusual%20scale%2C%20as%20most%20multibillion-dollar%20verdicts%20in%20the%20U.S.%20involve%20large%20corporations.%20The%20final%20distribution%20of%20the%20award%20hinges%20on%20the%20unpredictable%20real%20estate%20market%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20decline%20in%20apartment%20prices%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Jogani%20family's%20wealth%20originated%20from%20the%20global%20diamond%20trade%2C%20with%20Shashikant%20%26quot%3BShashi%26quot%3B%20Jogani%20establishing%20a%20successful%20gem%20business%20in%20California.%20The%20recession%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20and%20the%201994%20Northridge%20Earthquake%20prompted%20Shashi%20to%20involve%20his%20brothers%20in%20managing%20the%20firm%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20expansion%20of%20their%20property%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20the%20dispute%20is%20Haresh%20Jogani's%20alleged%20removal%20of%20Shashi%20Jogani%20from%20firm%20management%20without%20fair%20compensation%2C%20sparking%20a%20breach%20of%20their%20partnership.%20While%20Haresh%20argued%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20written%20agreement%2C%20the%20jury%20found%20him%20guilty%20of%20breaking%20a%20verbal%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20verdict%20details%20damages%20of%20%24165%20million%20for%20Haresh's%20breach%20of%20the%20diamond%20partnership%20with%20Chetan%20and%20Rajesh%2C%20along%20with%20%241.8%20billion%20to%20Shashi%2C%20%24234%20million%20to%20Chetan%2C%20and%20%24360%20million%20to%20Rajesh%20for%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20partnership.%20The%20jury%20also%20determined%20ownership%20percentages%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20partnership%3A%20Shashi%20holds%2050%20per%20cent%2C%20Haresh%2024%20per%20cent%2C%20Rajesh%2010%20per%20cent%2C%20Shailesh%209.5%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20Chetan%206.5%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20continue%2C%20the%20Jogani%20brothers'%20extensive%20real%20estate%20portfolio%2C%20generating%20up%20to%20%24137%20million%20annually%2C%20remains%20central%20to%20this%20intricate%20and%20protracted%20dispute.%20The%20case%20titled%20Jogani%20v.%20Jogani%20unfolds%20in%20the%20California%20Superior%20Court%2C%20Los%20Angeles%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Ff3n8l6vg_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplainer-property-dispute-between-the-jogani-brothers-ends-in-multibillion-dollar-verdict-5162758%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20legal%20dispute%2C%20known%20as%20Jogani%20v.%20Jogani%2C%20stems%20from%20accusations%20that%20Haresh%20Jogani%20violated%20a%20longstanding%20partnership%20with%20his%20siblings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplainer-property-dispute-between-the-jogani-brothers-ends-in-multibillion-dollar-verdict-5162758%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplainer-property-dispute-between-the-jogani-brothers-ends-in-multibillion-dollar-verdict-5162758%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplainer-property-dispute-between-the-jogani-brothers-ends-in-multibillion-dollar-verdict-5162758%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ship%20earlier%20attacked%20by%20Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20sinks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108163901%2Cimgsize-747154.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fship-earlier-attacked-by-yemens-houthi-rebels-sinks-in-the-red-sea%2Farticleshow%2F108163825.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108163825.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20ship%20targeted%20by%20Houthi%20rebels%20from%20Yemen%20has%20sunk%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20after%20sustaining%20damage%20over%20several%20days.%20This%20marks%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20a%20vessel%20being%20completely%20destroyed%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Houthi%20campaign%20linked%20to%20Israel's%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fship-earlier-attacked-by-yemens-houthi-rebels-sinks-in-the-red-sea%2Farticleshow%2F108163825.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fship-earlier-attacked-by-yemens-houthi-rebels-sinks-in-the-red-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F108163825.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fship-earlier-attacked-by-yemens-houthi-rebels-sinks-in-the-red-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F108163825.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Has%20Eliminated%20Extreme%20Poverty%2C%20Says%20US%20Think%20Tank%20Brookings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20think%20tank%20Brookings%20Institution%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20report%2C%20lauded%20India%20for%20eliminating%20extreme%20poverty%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20nation's%20socio-economic%20landscape.%20Authored%20by%20economists%20Surjit%20Bhalla%20and%20Karan%20Bhasin%2C%20the%20report%20attributes%20the%20achievement%20to%20the%20Indian%20government's%20robust%20policy%20initiatives%20focused%20on%20redistribution%2C%20fostering%20inclusive%20growth%20throughout%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20puts%20out%20statistics%20that%20show%20a%20substantial%20decline%20in%20the%20headcount%20poverty%20ratio%20and%20a%20surge%20in%20household%20consumption.%20The%20data%20presented%20challenges%20to%20previous%20estimates%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20indicating%20a%20lower%20number%20of%20impoverished%20individuals%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20pivotal%20factors%20contributing%20to%20this%20success%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%2C%20is%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20high%20economic%20growth%20and%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20income%20inequality.%20The%20'headcount%20poverty%20ratio%20at%20the%20purchase%20power%20parity%20%241.9%20level%20plummeted%20from%2012.2%25%20in%202011-12%20to%20a%20mere%202%25%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20asserted%20that%20the%20elevated%20consumption%20growth%20in%20rural%20areas%20is%20a%20direct%20outcome%20of%20the%20government's%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20redistribution.%20Publicly%20funded%20initiatives%2C%20such%20as%20the%20national%20mission%20for%20constructing%20toilets%20and%20the%20drive%20for%20universal%20access%20to%20electricity%2C%20modern%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20and%20piped%20water%2C%20have%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20impact%20of%20such%20policies%2C%20the%20report%20notes%20a%20staggering%20increase%20in%20rural%20access%20to%20piped%20water%20from%2016.8%25%20in%20August%202019%20to%20an%20impressive%2074.7%25%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20emphasise%20that%20the%20elimination%20of%20extreme%20poverty%20in%20India%20not%20only%20heralds%20positive%20implications%20for%20global%20poverty%20rates%20but%20also%20signals%20the%20need%20for%20the%20nation%20to%20graduate%20to%20a%20higher%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20two%20of%20the%20world's%20leading%20economies%20-%20Japan%20and%20the%20UK%20-%20have%20slipped%20into%20recession.%20Britain%20recently%20revealed%20a%200.3%20percent%20contraction%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%20and%20has%20officially%20entered%20a%20recession.%20Japan%2C%20once%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20largest%20economy%2C%20has%20also%20been%20struggling%20to%20recover%20after%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20which%20crippled%20the%20country's%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spotlight%20has%20now%20turned%20on%20India%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20opportunity%20for%20investors.%20Projections%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20suggest%20that%20India%20is%20poised%20to%20overtake%20both%20Japan%20and%20Germany%20in%20terms%20of%20economic%20output%2C%20with%20estimates%20placing%20the%20shift%20in%202026%20and%202027%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F8fsttk8s_sarojini-market-delhi_625x300_02_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-eliminated-extreme-poverty-says-us-think-tank-brookings-5162867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20American%20think%20tank%20Brookings%20Institution%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20report%2C%20lauded%20India%20for%20eliminating%20extreme%20poverty%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20nation's%20socio-economic%20landscape.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-eliminated-extreme-poverty-says-us-think-tank-brookings-5162867%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-eliminated-extreme-poverty-says-us-think-tank-brookings-5162867%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-eliminated-extreme-poverty-says-us-think-tank-brookings-5162867%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Gambhir%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Jayant%20Sinha%20makes%20exit%20from%20LS%20polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709380358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108163773%2Cimgsi