%25%20to%2026%25%20on%20in-app%20payments.%20Indian%20startups%20have%20long%20protested%20against%20what%20they%20deem%20as%20unfair%20practices%20by%20the%20US%20tech%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatrimony.com%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Bharat%20Matrimony%2C%20Christian%20Matrimony%2C%20Muslim%20Matrimony%2C%20and%20Jodii%2C%20expressed%20dismay%20as%20its%20matchmaking%20apps%20were%20taken%20down%20from%20Google's%20Play%20Store.%20Founder%20Murugavel%20Janakiraman%20referred%20to%20it%20as%20a%20dark%20day%20for%20India's%20internet%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20potential%20widespread%20impact%20on%20matrimony%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20apps%20are%20getting%20deleted%20one%20by%20one.%20It%20literally%20means%20all%20the%20top%20matrimony%20services%20will%20be%20deleted%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Janakiraman%20said%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20protect%20Indian%20startup%20ecosytem%20and%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20convey%20the%20same%20to%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%20big%20and%20vibrant%20startup%20ecosystem.%20We%20should%20take%20all%20steps%20to%20see%20that%20this%20ecosystem%20is%20protected.%20Google%20has%20been%20a%20good%20adopter%20of%20Indian%20technologies.%20I%20am%20quite%20hopeful%20that%20Google%20will%20be%20reasonable%20with%20its%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20told%20NDTV%20before%20he%20met%20Google%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Google%20briefly%20removed%20popular%20Indian%20payments%20app%20Paytm%20from%20its%20Play%20Store%20citing%20some%20policy%20violations.%20The%20move%20led%20to%20the%20company's%20founder%20and%20the%20wider%20startup%20industry%20joining%20together%20to%20challenge%20Google%20by%20launching%20their%20own%20app%20stores%20and%20filing%20legal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709379300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22