d%20the%20rest%20were%20dissatisfied%20over%20%26quot%3Btrivial%20issues%26quot%3B.%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20held%20discussions%20with%20the%20six%20disqualified%20MLAs%20and%20the%20situation%20would%20%26quot%3Bsurely%20get%20better%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20coordination%20committee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20cross-voting%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20for%20the%20lone%20seat%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Mr%20Rana%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20took%20this%20decision%20to%20uphold%20the%20honour%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20its%20people.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDid%20the%20Congress%20not%20have%20any%20candidate%20from%20the%20party%20workers%20in%20the%20state%20who%20could%20represent%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20cross-voting%20if%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20contested%20the%20polls%20instead%20of%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20Mr%20Rana%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20contributions%20to%20the%20country%20and%20been%20Congress%20president.%20Had%20she%20fought%20from%20here%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20different%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stunning%20upset%20for%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20on%20Tuesday%20won%20the%20state's%20lone%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20with%20its%20candidate%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20defeating%20Congress%20stalwart%20Singhvi%20and%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20no-trust%20motion%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20disqualified%20Congress%20MLA%20Inder%20Dutt%20Lakhanpal%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20now%20call%20us%20rebels%20or%20traitors.%20But%20we%20aren't.%20We%20listened%20to%20our%20conscience.%20It%20was%20our%20personal%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sukhu%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BEighty%20per%20cent%20of%20t