%20offices%20of%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20have%20finalised%20tenders%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Tripura%2C%20and%20Meghalaya%20for%20procuring%20%E2%80%9Cwoven%20laminated%20bags%20with%20an%20indicative%20logo%20of%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%9D%20to%20distribute%20food%20grains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20RTI%20reply%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20West%20Bengal%20region%2C%20selection%20of%20company%20for%20production%20of%20bags%20is%20under%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Rajasthan%20FCI%20office%20is%20spending%20Rs%2013.29%20crore%20for%201.07%20crore%20synthetic%20bags%2C%20for%20Tripura%2C%20Rs%2085.51%20lakh%20is%20being%20spent%20on%205.98%20lakh%20Modi-branded%20bags.%20The%20Meghalaya%20regional%20office%20is%20spending%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2052.75%20lakh%20for%204.22%20lakh%20bags%20and%20for%20Mizoram%2C%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20is%20being%20spent%20for%20procuring%201.75-lakh%20such%20bags%2C%20as%20per%20the%20RTI%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20process%20is%20pending%20as%20bags%20are%20still%20being%20produced%20while%20a%20private%20company%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20supply.%20The%20FCI%20is%20looking%20to%20procure%2098%2C000%20bags%20at%20Rs%2014.65%20apiece%2C%20totalling%20Rs%2014.35%20lakh%20in%20this%20eastern%20state%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20added%2C%20as%20per%20the%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20per%20piece%20procurement%20cost%20of%20the%20bags%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20logo%20is%20slightly%20different%20in%20each%20state.%20While%20each%20bag%20in%20Sikkim%20is%20being%20bought%20by%20the%20FCI%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2014.65%2C%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20Tripura%20it%20is%20at%20Rs%2014.30%20apiece%2C%20Rs%2012.5%20per%20per%20bag%20in%20Meghalaya%20and%20Rs%2012.375%20per%20bag%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.i