20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fpriests-association-condemns-politics-over-temples-2909771%5C%22%3Eanti-Hindu%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20alleging%20that%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20police%20personnel%20had%20removed%20a%20Hanuman%20flag%20from%20a%20flag%20post%20in%20the%20Keragodu%20village%20of%20Mandya.%20However%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20flag%20post%20was%20on%20government%20land%2C%20on%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Fhindi%2Fflag-row-in-karanatkas-mandya-how-ani-misled-its-audience-by-using-state-bjp-chiefs-erroneous-statement%2F%5C%22%3Eonly%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20the%20flag%20of%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20permitted%20to%20be%20hoisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20of%20diverting%20money%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20Karnataka%20was%20appointing%20non-Hindus%20in%20the%20temple%20trusts%20by%20amending%20the%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20%26amp%3B%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997%2C%20and%20taking%2010%25%20of%20the%20donations%20received%20by%20Hindu%20temples%20as%20tax.%20It%20is%20also%20claimed%20that%20according%20to%20the%20amendment%2C%20donations%20received%20by%20temples%20and%20others%20can%20also%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20any%20religious%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20related%20but%20distinct%20claims%20in%20these%20allegations%2C%20which%3Cem%3E%20Alt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20investigate%20in%20this%20report%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHas%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20started%20taxing%20Hindu%20temples%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIs%20the%20amount%20collected%20as%20tax%20on%20donations%20to%20Hindu%20temples%20(10%25)%20being%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20%E2%80%98any%E2%80%99%20religion%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIs%20money%20collected%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20being%20diverted%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20minority%20communities%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHas%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20amended%20the%20laws%20and%20introduced%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20in%20temple%20trusts%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews18%20anchor%20Rahul%20Shivshankar%20tweeted%20on%20February%2016%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20had%20allocated%20Rs%20330%20crore%20in%20the%20Budget%20for%20the%20development%20of%20Waqf%20property%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20Haj%20Bhawan%20in%20Mangalore%2C%20and%20the%20community%20development%20for%20Christians.%20In%20the%20same%20tweet%2C%20he%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20state%20government%20pocketed%20an%20average%20Rs%20450%20crores%20worth%20of%20annual%20donations%20by%20Hindu%20devotees%20to%20400%20%E2%80%98A%20%26amp%3B%20B%E2%80%99%20category%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20from%20Bangalore%20South%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20quote-tweeted%20this%20post%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20took%20money%20from%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20was%20using%20it%20to%20fund%20religious%20institutions%20that%20were%20non-Hindu.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20money%20of%20Hindus%20was%20being%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20economically%20enrich%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETo%20take%20money%20from%20the%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20use%20it%20to%20fund%20the%20religious%20institutions%20of%20non%20Hindu%20faiths%20is%20the%20standard%20SOP%20of%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20leaders%20like%20Siddharamiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecularism%20as%20practiced%20by%20them%20is%20not%20just%20a%20stick%20to%20brow%20beat%20the%20Hindu%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20tool%20to%20financially%20enrich%E2%80%A