ndu%20Religious%20Institutions%20and%20Charitable%20Endowments%20Act%2C%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Dharmarika%20Parishad%20has%20the%20power%20to%20create%20a%20common%20pool%20fund%20in%20which%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20income%20of%20big%20temples%20and%20grants%20received%20from%20the%20state%20government%20would%20be%20contributed%20for%20the%20maintenance%20of%20small%20and%20low%20income%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20and%20religious%20institutions%20of%20Hindus%20falling%20within%20the%20Muzrai%20department.%20Grants%20were%20created%20to%20build%20orphanages%20for%20Hindus%2C%20construction%20of%20cowsheds%2C%20the%20study%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20amendment%20made%20in%202011%2C%20the%20tax%20rates%20on%20temples%20were%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E0%25%20of%20the%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20was%20less%20than%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E5%25%20of%20the%20net%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20exceeded%20Rs%205%20lakh%20but%20did%20not%20exceed%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E10%25%20of%20the%20net%20income%20of%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20was%20more%20than%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20amendment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20no%20common%20pool%20fund%20for%20temples%20whose%20annual%20income%20is%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20temples%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20between%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20a%20total%20of%205%25%20of%20their%20annual%20income%20would%20go%20to%20the%20common%20pool%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20temples%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20above%2C%20a%20total%20of%2010%25%20would%20go%20to%20the%20common%20pool%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20working%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20shared%20a%20file%20with%20%3C