ust%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20noticed%20the%20point%20highlighted%20by%20BJP%20IT%20cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya.%20The%20provision%20he%20highlighted%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20non-Hindus%20to%20the%20temple%20trust%20had%20actually%20been%20enacted%20prior%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20under%20present%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20recent%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20do%20these%20lines%20state%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20committee%20shall%20consist%20of%20at%20least%20one%20person%20resident%20in%20the%20locality%20where%20the%20institution%20is%20situated%3A%20Provided%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20composite%20institution%2C%20members%20of%20both%20Hindu%20and%20other%20religions%20may%20be%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20a%20composite%20institution%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20information%20given%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F7825%2F1%2F33_of_2001_%2528e%2529.pdf%5C%22%3Epoint%2010A%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20definition%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ecomposite%20institution%3C%2Fem%3E%20denotes%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20common%20and%20jointly%20maintained%20by%20Hindus%20and%20other%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20this%20issue%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Muzrai%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fno-diversion-of-temple-funds-let-bjp-leaders-read-law-first-ramalinga-reddy-karnataka-minister-for-transport-muzrai%2Farticleshow%2F107917058.cms%5C%22%3ERamalinga%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20viral%20claim%20about%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20introducing%20a%20provision%20to%20appoint%20non-Hindus%20to%20temple%20trusts%20was%20misleading.%20Only%20the%20committees%20of%20Baba%20Budan%20Giri%20Dargah%20in%20Chikmagalur%20district%2C%20Bhootrai%20Chowdeshwari%20and%20Saadat%20Ali%20Dargah%20in%20Shivamogga%20district%20consisted%20of%20members%20from%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20because%20people%20of%20both%20the%20religions%20prayed%20at%20these%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%2C%20but%20due%20to%20opposition%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%2C%20it%20could%20not%20be%20passed%20in%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTempleTaxBill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TempleTaxBill%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbwtDEEkDGI%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbwtDEEkDGI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1761087964543889496%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Akhila%20Karnataka%20Archakas%20(Priests%E2%80%99)%20Association%20supported%20the%20Bill%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20and%20said%20that%20small%20temples%20were%20short%20of%20funds.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20it%20urged%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20to%20support%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20divert%20tax%20money%20from%20rich%20A%20grade%20temples%20to%20smaller%20temples%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%2036%2C000%20C%20grade%20temples%20in%20the%20state%2C%20categorized%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20All%20Karnataka%20Hindu%20Temple%20Archaka%20(priest)%20Association%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20receiving%20a%20sum%20of%20only%20Rs%205%2C000%20as%20our%20salary%2C%20which%20is%20inclusive%20of%20puja%20materials.%20No%20one%20has%20raised%20a%20strong%20voice%20for%20us%20like%20the%20current%20Muzrai%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy.%20The%20money%20from%20the%20Common%20Pool%20Fund%20will%20be%20used%20only%20for%20the%20uplift%20of%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20grade%20temples%20and%20priests.%20We%20are%20very%20happy%20with%20this%20decision.%E2%80%9D%20The%20association%20also%20decided%20to%20submit%20a%20memorandum%20to%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20leaders%2C%20urging%20them%20not%20to%20oppose%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20current%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.altnews.in%2Ftruth-of-rumors-around-karnatakas-new-hindu-religious-endowments-amendment-bill%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20Alt%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709307036000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F01195125%2Fimage-1892.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-is-the-karnataka-temple-tax-legislation-the-claims-counterclaims-and-facts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20targeted%20the%20Karnataka%20Congress%20government%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20appeasement%20of%20the%20minority%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-is-the-karnataka-temple-tax-legislation-the-claims-counterclaims-and-facts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Learn%20Pottery%20%26amp%3B%20Mandana%20Art%20at%20this%20Rajasthan%20Eco-Lodge%20That%20Runs%20on%20The%20Sun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20renowned%20for%20its%20rich%20tapestry%20of%20diverse%20cultures%2C%20and%20one%20of%20its%20most%20vibrant%20states%20is%20Rajasthan.%20Situated%20in%20the%20northwestern%20region%20of%20the%20country%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341177%2Fchhotaram-prajapat-mud-homestay-in-salawas-village-jodhpur-rajasthan-dhurrie-making%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajasthan%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20opulent%20and%20vibrant%20lifestyle%20of%20its%20rulers%20throughout%20history.%20Adorned%20with%20majestic%20palaces%2C%20vibrant%20markets%2C%20and%20timeless%20traditions%2C%20each%20city%20within%20the%20state%20weaves%20together%20a%20tapestry%20of%20music%2C%20dance%2C%20art%2C%20and%20cuisine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20not%20visited%20this%20outstanding%20example%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20rich%20culture%20and%20heritage%20yet%2C%20then%20this%20is%20your%20sign!%20Every%20niche%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20state%20has%20something%20unique%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20cultural%20splendour%2C%20there%20is%20an%20array%20of%20resorts%20and%20hotels%20that%20offer%20visitors%20the%20quintessential%20Rajasthani%20experience%2C%20but%20there%20is%20one%20you%20cannot%20miss.%20Among%20the%20myriad%20high-end%20establishments%20of%20the%20state%20stands%20a%20labour%20of%20love%20%E2%80%93%20Apani%20Dhani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApani%20Dhani%20is%20the%20manifestation%20of%20Ramesh%20Chandra%20Jangid%E2%80%99s%20two%20passions%20%E2%80%93%20serving%20people%20and%20preserving%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20deeply%20committed%20to%20the%20preservation%20of%20nature%20while%20simultaneously%20supporting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97986%2Ffree-legal-aid-cells-goa-vm-salgaocar-college-law%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20commun