ors%20help%20facilitate%20such%20admissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20additional%20coaching%20classes%20at%20the%20daycare%20centre%20where%20teachers%20take%20tuition%20to%20enhance%20the%20foundational%20learning%20that%20gets%20affected%20because%20of%20late%20schooling%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20NGO%20also%20provides%20age-appropriate%20pre-learning%20activities%20and%20education.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1-1709217253-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343607%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20NGO%20also%20provides%20age-appropriate%20pre-learning%20activities%20and%20education.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20non-profit%20also%20conducts%20various%20non-academic%20activities%20to%20capture%20their%20interest%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20painting%2C%20street%20plays%2C%20sports%20and%20music-related%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjusha%20informs%20that%20the%20non-profit%20continues%20to%20assist%20these%20children%20until%20the%20construction%20work%20nears%20completion.%20The%20m