Cp%3EThis%20was%20what%20prodded%20the%20team%20to%20begin%20thinking%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303089%2Faditya-raj-artist-sketches-heritage-restaurants-iconic-spots-in-mumbai-delhi-kyani-nirulas-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroducing%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20more%20inclusive%20space.%20And%20they%20say%20the%20Rajasthan%20Netraheen%20Kalyan%20Sangh%20was%20ideal%20to%20champion%20this%20cause.%20Since%201968%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20been%20working%20with%20blind%20persons%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20for%20students%20to%20excel%20at%20education%20along%20with%20gaining%20essential%20life%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20quest%20for%20holistic%20development%20that%20drew%20the%20St%2Bart%20India%20Foundation%20to%20it%2C%20and%20Project%20Sparsh%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFeel%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20believe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20initiative%20was%20to%20enable%20the%20children%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinteract%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20art.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20beautiful%20range%20of%20colours%20and%20textures%20by%20Asian%20Paints%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20glorious%20strokes%20of%20paint%20and%20texture%20that%20are%20equally%20rich%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326377%2Fnoida-madhuri-balodi-amit-singh-kavi-the-poetry-art-project-glass-bottle-art-sustainability-home-decor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20compelling%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20put%20together%20in%20the%20prayer%20hall%20of%20the%20school%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20conveys%20the%20legacy%20of%20Rajasthani%20culture.%20The%20sensation%20of%20tactility%20is%20achieved%20through%20the%20Royale%20Play%20range%20of%20textured%20paints%20from%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20which%20turns%20simple%20surfaces%20into%20tactile%20language%20that%20the%20students%20can%20touch%20and%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20textured%20paints%20add%20a%20new%20dimension%20and%20redefine%20the%20art%2C%20says%20Amit%20Syngle%2C%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Asian%20Paints%20Ltd.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20we%20leverage%20art%20and%20creativity%20to%20foster%20inclusivity%20among%20people.%20Sparsh%20is%20a%20representation%20of%20our%20values%20of%20empathy%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20creativity.%20This%20initiative%20aims%20to%20bring%20joy%20and%20inspiration%20to%20visually%20impaired%20students%20through%20touch%20and%20feel.%20The%20murals%20narrate%20captivating%20stories%2C%20from%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Rajasthan%20to%20the%20indomitable%20spirit%20of%20Helen%20Keller%20and%20are%20accessible%20to%20all%2C%20especially%20people%20who%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperceive%20the%20world%20differently%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20us.%20Together%20with%20St%2Bart%20India%20Foundation%2C%20the%20Sparsh%20initiative%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20commitment%20to%20%23ArtForAll.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Finclusivity-in-art-6-1709208239.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20space%20is%20divided%20into%20an%20outdoor%20art%20mural%2C%20an%20indoor%20art%20museum%20and%20an%20art%20workshop%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Finclusivity-in-art-6-1709208239.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Finclusivity-in-art-6-1709208239-300x157.jp