ividuals%20involved%20in%20the%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20required%20us%20to%20ask%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20and%20really%20break%20through%20what%20we%20knew%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20person%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Project%20Sparsh%20testifies%20that%20it%20reaffirmed%20the%20belief%20that%20art%20is%20a%20universal%20language%2C%20speaking%20to%20each%20individual%E2%80%99s%20senses%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709215793000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343534%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sparsh%2C%20an%20initiative%20by%20Asian%20Paints%20and%20St%2Bart%20Foundation%2C%20is%20transforming%20Jaipur%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthan%20Netraheen%20Kalyan%20Sangh%20Institute%20into%20a%20place%20where%20visually%20impaired%20children%20can%20appreciate%20art.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343534%2Fsparsh-asian-paints-start-foundation-initiative-tactile-art-rajasthan-netraheen-kalyan-sangh-jaipur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ticket%20Collector%20to%20UPSC%20Officer%20to%20Shark%20Tank%3A%20Founder%20Won%20Rs%2045%20Lakh%20for%20Anti-Theft%20Luggage%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20us%20know%20someone%20who%20has%20lost%20a%20wallet%20or%20a%20bag%20during%20our%20travels.%20It%20might%20be%20because%20they%20left%20it%20or%20it%20got%20stolen.%20Pickpocketing%20and%20luggage%20theft%20cases%20are%20unfortunately%20a%20common%20occurrence%20while%20commuting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20case%20of%20pickpocketing%20made%20Atul%20Gupta%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Arista%20Vault%20rethink%20the%20way%20people%20look%20at%20travel%20safety.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20my%20wallet%20stolen%20on%20the%20Delhi%20metro%20and%20was%20technically%20stranded%20with%20no%20money%20on%20my%20way%20to%20an%20important%20event.%20This%20triggered%20a%20thought%20and%20I%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas%20on%20how%20we%20can%20make%20travelling%20safer%20using%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECo-founded%20by%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%20Roy%2C%20the%20startup%20makes%20products%20that%20make%20our%20travel%20safer.%20From%20smart%20wallets%20to%20luggage%2C%20it%20has%20made%20travelling%20safer%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20duo%20won%20the%20sharks%20over%20at%20the%20TV%20show%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20and%20won%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2045%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20Unique%20Journey%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20unique%20products%2C%20what%20is%20interesting%20is%20the%20journey%20the%20founders%20had%20before%20collaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2039%2C%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20career%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20my%20batch%20to%20clear%20the%20Railways%20exams%20and%20got%20posted%20as%20a%20ticket%20collector.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20lost%20their%20luggage%20to%20theft.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20distress%20and%20loss%20it%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20and%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259714%2Fwest-bengal-history-woman-bela-mitra-brave-india-freedom-struggle-british-raj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20the%20railways%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Atul%20also%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20to%20become%20a%20government%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20managing%20both%20things%20and%20I%20failed%20four%20times%20before%20cracking%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20served%20as%20an%20officer%2C%20conducting%20audits%20of%20national%20Navratna%20companies%20and%20Maharatna%20PSUs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20This%20marked%20around%2013-14%20years%20into%20my%20service.%20While%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20servant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20yearned%20to%20create%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20has%20launched%20smart%20wallet%20which%20anti-theft%20and%20enables%20you%20to%20track%20its%20location.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-4-1709213062-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343569%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20has%20launched%20a%20smart%20wallet%20which%20anti-theft%20and%20enables%20you%20to%20track%20its%20location.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Atul%20wanted%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20himself.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20huge%20decision%20to%20take%20an%20early%20retirement%20but%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20direction%20of%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20his%20wallet%20got%20stolen%20when%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20an%20event.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20at%20this%20event%20that%20I%20met%20my%20co-founder%20who%20was%20herself%20in%20a%20similar%20dilemma%20as%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Purvi%20was%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311375%2Fvishakha-asana-angrakha-size-inclusive-fashion-clothing-brand-fat-tax-shark-tank-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efashion%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20designed%20clothing%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20office%20wear.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20have%20quite%20a%20fight%20to%20become%20a%20designer%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20My%20family%20was%20always%20against%20my%20decision%20and%20wanted%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20traditional%20degree.%20However%2C%20after%20all%20the%20fights%2C%20I%20did%20not%20find%20my%20work%20to%20be%20fulfilling.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20dilemma%20and%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20had%20some%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20duo%20met%20and%20Atul%20expressed%20how%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20around%20travel%20safety%2C%20Purvi%20decided%20to%20jump%20on%20the%20opportunity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20we%20both%20decided%20to%20collaborate%20to%20start%20Arista%20Vault%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Atul%20and%20Purvi%20along%20with%20their%20friend%2C%20Col%20Krishan%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20started%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMerging%20travel%20safety%20with%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20how%20their%20brainstorming%20would%20go%2C%20Atul%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20inspired%20and%20triggered%20by%20my%20stolen%20wallet%2C%20so%20that%20is%20what%20we%20first%20tried%20to%20develop%20%E2%80%93%20a%20smart%20wallet.%20The%20smart%20wallet%20has%20a%20chip%20which%20once%20activated%20becomes%20anti-theft.%20They%20have%203000mAh%20Power%20charging%2C%20location%20tracking%20and%20RFID%20protection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20various%20types%20of%20products%20they%20make%2C%20Purvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%20we%20have%20three%20categories%20of%20products.%20We%20have%20smart%20wallets%20with%20different%20price%20ranges%20and%20variants.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20bag%20with%20fingerprint%20locks.%20These%20bags%20are%20designed%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205523%2Fdispose-electronic-electrical-waste-india-ewaste-old-laptops-batteries-phone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20store%20your%20laptops%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20other%20valuables%20and%20can%20be%20locked%20with%20a%20fingerprint.%20Only%20the%20owner%20can%20access%20the%20bag%20once%20it%20is%20locked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC37mvNmsDu0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC37mvNmsDu0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC37mvNmsDu0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Arista%20Vault%20%7C%20TECH%20%7C%20LUXURY%20%7C%20TRAVEL%20%7C%20(%40aristavault)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20category%20of%20products%20is%20smart%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20luggage%20is%20not%20just%20anti-theft%20but%20it%20also%20has%20various%20other%20features.%20The%20luggage%20has%20a%20%E2%80%98follow%20me%E2%80%99%20option%20in%20which%20it%20detects%20your%20motions%20and%20follows%20you.%20This%20way%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20drag%20it%20around.%20You%20can%20also%20ride%20on%20it%20for%205%20km.%20The%20advanced%20AI%20sensors%20ensure%20smooth%20movement%2C%20and%20prioritising%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Robo%20suitcase%E2%80%99%2C%20Purvi%20says%20that%20it%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20and%20best%20selling%20product%20on%20their%20website.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20very%20intrigued%20by%20it%20and%20the%20sales%20of%20the%20suitcase%20have%20been%20the%20highest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20experiencing%20more%20demand%20from%20the%20Southern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20product%20delivers%20what%20it%20claims.%20You%20know%20how%20you%20keep%20losing%20your%20wallet%20here%20and%20there.%20The%20problem%20is%20no%20longer%20an%20issue%20for%20me%20because%20I%20can%20easily%20track%20it%20with%20my%20phone.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20the%20charging%20facility%20so%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20my%20phone%20dying%20as%20I%20can%20charge%20it%20on%20the%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aqib%2C%20a%20customer%20who%20purchased%20their%20smart%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20duo%20went%20on%20to%20Shark%20Tank%20and%20charmed%20all%20the%20sharks.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20at%20the%20show%2C%20our%20luggage%20was%20the%20star%20of%20the%20evening.%20All%20the%20sharks%20loved%20riding%20on%20it%20and%20they%20kept%20moving%20it%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20happily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20their%20experience%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20experience%20was%20amazing.%20Before%20entering%2C%20we%20were%20very%20nervous%20and%20my%20hands%20were%20sweating%20but%20once%20we%20started%20talking%2C%20all%20my%20anxieties%20went%20away.%20Although%20the%20sharks%20had%20a%20few%20doubts%20about%20the%20market%20of%20the%20products%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20convince%20them.%20We%20went%20inside%20to%20crack%20a%20deal%20and%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20could%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-5-1709213260.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20duo%20were%20able%20to%20bag%20a%20Shark%20Tank%20deal%20of%20Rs%2045%20Lakhs.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-5-1709213260.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEIY-5-1709213260-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th