C%20until%20it%20reaches%20a%20thick%2C%20porridge-like%20consistency.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20slow%20cooking%20process%2C%20often%20lasting%20several%20hours%2C%20allows%20the%20flavours%20to%20meld%20together%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20rich%20and%20velvety%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20hundreds%20of%20people%20visiting%20the%20place%20everyday%2C%20you%20should%20try%20Pista%20House%E2%80%99s%20haleem%20at%20least%20once%20in%20your%20life.%20Garnished%20with%20fried%20onions%2C%20fresh%20cilantro%2C%20mint%20leaves%2C%20and%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lemon%2C%20Pista%20House%20Haleem%20is%20a%20feast%20for%20the%20senses%2C%20captivating%20diners%20with%20its%20irresistible%20aroma%20and%20sumptuous%20taste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Haleem%20-%20a%20must-try%20dish%20of%20Hyderabad.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHaleem%20%E2%80%93%20a%20must-try%20dish%20of%20Hyderabad.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Pathar%20ka%20Gosht%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20have%20not%20tried%20the%20delicious%20Pathar%20Ka%20Gosht%2C%20your%20trip%20is%20incomplete.%20Pathar%20ka%20Gosht%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%9CMeat%20cooked%20on%20stone%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20prepared%20by%20cooking%20marinated%20meat%20on%20a%20hot%20stone%2C%20infusing%20it%20with%20a%20unique%20smoky%20flavour%20and%20tender%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20meat%20cooks%20on%20the%20hot%20stone%2C%20it%20absorbs%20the%20heat%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20seared%20exterior%20and%20a%20juicy%2C%20succulent%20interior.%20If%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20try%20them%2C%20then%20Bade%20Miyan%20Kabab%20is%20the%20answer.%20According%20to%20a%20News18%20article%2C%20the%20place%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(the%20restaurant)%20have%20been%20following%20the%20recipe%20since%201954%2C%20encompassing%20two%20generations.%20The%20tradition%20of%20making%20Patthar%20Ka%20Gosht%20is%20said%20to%20date%20way%20back%20to%20the%20Nizam%20era.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pathar%20Ka%20Gosht%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343312%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%2