in%20these%20cleaners%2C%20which%20posed%20risks%20to%20her%20daughter%20and%20even%20the%20surfaces%20they%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20longer%20at%20ease%20with%20her%20daughter%20participating%20in%20cleaning%20activities%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20exposure%20to%20these%20toxic%20chemicals%2C%20Simran%2C%20a%20concerned%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20and%20an%20MBA%20graduate%20with%2014%20years%20of%20corporate%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20resolved%20to%20develop%20a%20line%20of%20eco-friendly%20home%20cleaners%20that%20would%20prioritise%20child%20and%20pet%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20Simran%20Khara%2C%20the%20former%20CEO%20of%20Juggernaut%20Books%2C%20launched%20Koparo%20Clean%20in%20February%202021.%20Koparo%20Clean%20is%20a%20home-care%20product%20brandboasting%20of%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%E2%80%9D%20formulations%20crafted%20from%20plant-based%20ingredients%20such%20as%20coconuts%20(%3Cem%3Ekopra%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20gained%20national%20attention%20when%20she%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%203%2C%20where%20she%20secured%20a%20substantial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20from%20%E2%80%98Sharks%E2%80%99%20Vineeta%20Singh%20and%20Aman%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20search%20of%20a%20toxin-free%20cleaning%20product%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201067px)%20100vw%2C%201067px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Simran%20started%20Koparo%20as%20she%20wanted%20her%20daughter%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20toxin-free%20cleaners%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181.jpeg%201067w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-768x1152.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-1024x1536.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkoparo-1708954181-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESimran%20started%20Koparo%20as%20she%20wanted%20her%20daughter%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20toxin-free%20cleaners%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20so%20wrong%20with%20the%20cleaners%20we%20use%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conventional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337481%2Fbaljeet-kaur-mountaineer-climber-mt-annapurna-everest-kilimanjaro-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20commonly%20used%20in%20households%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20floor%20cleaners%2C%20dishwashing%20liquids%2C%20and%20laundry%20detergents%20boasting%20of%20clothes%20whitening%20capabilities%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20contain%20a%20combination%20of%20cleaning%20agents%2C%20fabric%20whiteners%2C%20sodium%20silicate%2C%20and%20sodium%20sulfate.%20A%20study%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EChemosphere%3C%2Fem%3E%20scrutinised%2030%20such%20cleaning%20products%20and%20revealed%20that%20they%20may%20emit%20hazardous%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20(VOCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20analysis%20highlighted%20that%20many%20of%20these%20VOCs%20pose%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20damage%20to%20the%20respiratory%20system%2C%20heightened%20cancer%20susceptibility%2C%20and%20adverse%20effects%20on%20developmental%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20Furthermore%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmental%20Working%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%20(EWG)%20cautioned%20that%20the%20fumes%20emanating%20from%20certain%20cleaning%20products%20could%20trigger%20asthma%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20recounts%20that%20during%20the%20first%2010%20to%2012%20weeks%20post-lockdown%2C%20she%2C%20like%20many%20other%20mothers%2C%20found%20herself%20relying%20heavily%20on%20cleaning%20products%20at%20home.%20She%20scrubbed%20surfaces%20multiple%20times%20to%20maintain%20a%20COVID-19-free%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20using%20cleaning%20liquids%20for%20washing%20our%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20everything%20else%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20hygiene%20took%20centre-stage%2C%20was%20it%20unknowingly%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20careful%20assessment%20of%20multiple%20research%20papers%20made%20Simran%20get%20up%20and%20take%20action.%20She%20looked%20for%20safer%20alternatives%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20many%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20same%20prices%20as%20the%20regular%20cleaning%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20ingredients.%20Discovering%20many%20chemical%20names%20in%20everyday%20products%20was%20triggering%20for%20me%2C%20as%20they%20posed%20harm%20to%20my%20daughter.%20While%20doing%20home%20cleaning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20first-hand%20experience%20of%20how%20it%20was%20affecting%20my%20hands.%20I%20could%20see%20exactly%20what%20was%20being%20put%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%E2%80%9D%20Simran%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20that%20she%20realised%20that%20most%20conventional%20cleaners%20were%20laden%20with%20toxins.%20Unable%20to%20find%20any%20alternatives%2C%20she%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20develop%20products%20that%20would%20provide%20reassurance%20to%20mothers%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab%20in%20Be